  <tr>
    <td colspan="1" valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5" color="black">
    Suffocating Sphere</font></td>
    <td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left"><font color="black"><img
    src="http://205.229.72.28/ev1/public_html/images/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right"></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=228">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=228">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Causes damage over a length of time which lowers strength. After casting,it initially causes 8 damage points to the target which is then followed for a random length of time by 10 HP every 4 seconds. STR & AGI are lowered by 5.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Lowers STR<BR>
Lowers AGI<BR>
Damage over time
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
			&nbsp;<br>
			&nbsp;<br>
			Mana:<br>
			Casting Time:<br>
			Target Type:<br>
			Level:<br>
			Rank:<br>
    </font></td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">

		  &nbsp;<br>
		  &nbsp;<br>
			20<br>
			2<br>
			Target<br>
			4<br>
			2<br>
    </font></td>
