	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The Suffocating Sphere is one of, if not the best combat spell that Enchanters can have before the 3rd ranks spells. It may seem to have little power, but this is the spell that I use most of the time to pick a fight.  It deals 10 damage at first, then slowly hurts the target over time, it is great when you are chasing an enemy that has run off.  It also lowers strength, so when combined with Enfeeblement, it can bring a burly gnoll to hit like a scrawny gnoll.  Every enchanter must have this spell to use.<BR>
<BR>
Skitsos of Bertoxxulous
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
